You're just beginners ♪

22:45.781 --> 22:49.326
♪ If you're not with us, you are against ♪

22:49.409 --> 22:52.579
♪ Yeah, you can't stop us or ever top us ♪

22:52.662 --> 22:56.208
♪ From the beginning until the end ♪

22:56.291 --> 22:57.709
♪ We will defend ♪

